ensure you have mozilla firefox

1. Start Apache and MySQL in your XAMPP Control Panel.
2. Go to http://localhost/phpmyadmin.
3. Create a new database named `bl_db_adet`.
4. Click on the `bl_db_adet` database, go to the "Import" tab, and import the included `README-SETUP/bl_db_adet.sql` file.
5. Ensure your BicoLikha Django server is running locally (run `python manage.py runserver` inside C:\Users\Justin\BicoLikha_adet).

run in terminal within this test folder:
python -m pip install pytest selenium webdriver-manager

run these to check all files:

py error_handling_test.py
py test_add_record.py
py test_helper.py
py test_login.py
py test_search.py
py test_validation.py
py test_order_cod.py
